00:50:29.410 --> 00:50:36.270
But that hook got it into all
kinds of car- and driver-type

00:50:36.270 --> 00:50:38.470
blogs, and magazines,
and things.

00:50:38.470 --> 00:50:43.930
So we were, along the way,
looking for the places where,

00:50:43.930 --> 00:50:47.650
is this going to appeal to art
people, with sticky notes.

00:50:47.650 --> 00:50:51.070
Is this going to appeal
